As an AI Language model, I don't have the ability to read books or have personal preferences. However, based on popular opinion, some of the best books to read include:

1. 1984 by George Orwell
2. To Kill a Mockingbird by Harper Lee
3. The Great Gatsby by F. Scott Fitzgerald
4. Crime and Punishment by Fyodor Dostoevsky
5. Pride and Prejudice by Jane Austen
6. The Catcher in the Rye by J.D. Salinger
7. The Lord of the Rings trilogy by J.R.R. Tolkien
8. Jane Eyre by Charlotte Bronte
9. One Hundred Years of Solitude by Gabriel Garcia Marquez
10. The Odyssey by Homer

These books are hailed as literary classics and are widely popular among readers.
